<p class="discreet" tal:define="portal_url context/portal_url">
    <tal:happy tal:condition="view/isHappy">
        <img tal:attributes="src string:${portal_url}/happy-face.png" alt="Happy Face" /><br />
        Having a Z in your title pleases me.
    </tal:happy>

    <tal:happy tal:condition="not:view/isHappy">
        <img tal:attributes="src string:${portal_url}/angry-face.png" alt="Angry Face" /><br />
        The lack of a Z in your title displeases me.
    </tal:happy>  

</p>